DESCRIPTION
RETURN VALUE
       Returns an xcb_void_cookie_t. Errors (if any) have to be handled in the event loop.

       If you want to handle errors directly with xcb_request_check instead, use xcb_dri3_pixmap_from_buffers_checked. See xcb-requests(3) for details.

